<li id="R3">
<span class="label">3.</span><cite>Vickers AJ, Brewster SF. PSA Velocity and Doubling Time in Diagnosis and Prognosis of Prostate Cancer. Br J Med Surg Urol. 2012;5(4):162–168. doi: 10.1016/j.bjmsu.2011.08.006.</cite> [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.bjmsu.2011.08.006" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI</a>] [<a href="/articles/PMC3375697/" class="usa-link">PMC free article</a>] [<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22712027/" class="usa-link">PubMed</a>] [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Br%20J%20Med%20Surg%20Urol&amp;title=PSA%20Velocity%20and%20Doubling%20Time%20in%20Diagnosis%20and%20Prognosis%20of%20Prostate%20Cancer&amp;author=AJ%20Vickers&amp;author=SF%20Brewster&amp;volume=5&amp;issue=4&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;pages=162-168&amp;pmid=22712027&amp;doi=10.1016/j.bjmsu.2011.08.006&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
<li id="R4">
<span class="label">4.</span><cite>Vickers AJ. Prostate cancer: why is PSA velocity such a sticky concept? Nat Rev Urol. 2013;10(4):189–190. doi: 10.1038/nrurol.2013.47.</cite> [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1038/nrurol.2013.47" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI</a>] [<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23478537/" class="usa-link">PubMed</a>] [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Nat%20Rev%20Urol&amp;title=Prostate%20cancer:%20why%20is%20PSA%20velocity%20such%20a%20sticky%20concept?&amp;author=AJ%20Vickers&amp;volume=10&amp;issue=4&amp;publication_year=2013&amp;pages=189-190&amp;pmid=23478537&amp;doi=10.1038/nrurol.2013.47&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
<li id="R5">
<span class="label">5.</span><cite>Orsted DD, et al.  Long-term prostate-specific antigen velocity in improved classification of prostate cancer risk and mortality. Eur Urol. 2013;64(3):384–393. doi: 10.1016/j.eururo.2013.01.028.</cite> [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.eururo.2013.01.028" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI</a>] [<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23398767/" class="usa-link">PubMed</a>] [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Eur%20Urol&amp;title=Long-term%20prostate-specific%20antigen%20velocity%20in%20improved%20classification%20of%20prostate%20cancer%20risk%20and%20mortality&amp;author=DD%20Orsted&amp;volume=64&amp;issue=3&amp;publication_year=2013&amp;pages=384-393&amp;pmid=23398767&amp;doi=10.1016/j.eururo.2013.01.028&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
<li id="R6">
<span class="label">6.</span><cite>Carter HB, Pearson JD. PSA velocity for the diagnosis of early prostate cancer. A new concept. Urol Clin North Am. 1993;20(4):665–670.</cite> [<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7505974/" class="usa-link">PubMed</a>] [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Urol%20Clin%20North%20Am&amp;title=PSA%20velocity%20for%20the%20diagnosis%20of%20early%20prostate%20cancer.%20A%20new%20concept&amp;author=HB%20Carter&amp;author=JD%20Pearson&amp;volume=20&amp;issue=4&amp;publication_year=1993&amp;pages=665-670&amp;pmid=7505974&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
<li id="R7">
